### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Register — create a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad Jaiswal",
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register — missing name (expect 422)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register — duplicate email (expect 409 after running Register above)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad Jaiswal",
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login — copy the token from the response
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login — wrong password (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### List users — valid token (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### List users — no token (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

###

### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Ketaki",
  "email": "ketaki@example.com"
}

###

### Get user — paste a real UUID from a previous response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/PASTE_USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get user — invalid UUID (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/PASTE_USER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Ketaki Updated",
  "email": "ketaki.updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete user (expect 204 no content)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/PASTE_USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE
